id windowtext; border-top-width: initial; border-top-style: none; background: #5b9bd5; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"289\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Payloads:</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 216.4pt; border-top-width: initial; border-top-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-left-style: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; background: #5b9bd5; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"289\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">OCM, SCAT , SSTM and ARGOS</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 216.4pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-top-width: initial; border-top-style: none; background: #5b9bd5; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"289\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Local time of Eq. crossing:</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 216.4pt; border-top-width: initial; border-top-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-left-style: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; background: #5b9bd5; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"289\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">12 noon</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 216.4pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-top-width: initial; border-top-style: none; background: #5b9bd5; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"289\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">Mass at lift off:</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 216.4pt; border-top-width: initial; border-top-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-left-style: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; background: #5b9bd5; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"289\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
